  <div class="ct">
  
<p>In my home town crotchety old pseudo-feminist elementary school teachers, neglected and punished boys for being boys. &nbsp;They were particularly hard on African American boys (that often had lower levels of support at home), and sent many down the wrong path. &nbsp;I say pseudo-feminist, because they believed in putting males into subservient roles to them, not bringing everyone (male and female) to the same high level.</p>

  </div>
