<p>So please drop the mythology of teachers' hours being better and of teacher pay being so fabu.</p>
<p>Fun? &nbsp;Sure? &nbsp;Rewarding? &nbsp;Absolutely. &nbsp;But I don't do it for the hours and I certainly don't do it for the money as, given my advanced education, I could make a lot more if I worked for a corporation.</p>

