   <h5> <a class="de">&nbsp;</a><span class="cu">My district addressed this disparity years ago.</span>


<span class="crd ntb">(<a href="/comments/1234916/51226832#c140?mode=alone;showrate=1#c140">6+ / 0-</a>)</span>
