  <div class="ct">
  
<p>I believe that teacher evaluations should involve a variety of measures. &nbsp;Student achievement should be a piece of it. &nbsp;Student achievement should encompass a variety of things including projects. &nbsp;This is more labor intensive on the part of those conducting the evaluations, but it would give a more accurate picture of the teacher's performance.</p>
