<p>An educator may be able to give another educator advice as to the <strong>process</strong> of the education, but your customers don't give a shit about the process at all. I literally don't care if teachers adhere or don't adhere to some pedagogy model or other, or if a principal likes or dislikes their classroom management, or whatever. I care <strong>only</strong> that the student <strong>knows math or science or writing or whatever</strong> at the end of the class.</p>
